    "description": "『The Dream Labyrinth』 is a single-player game that combines tower defense with roguelike elements.<br><br>The player enters the dreams of a girl named &quot;Asteria,&quot; who has lost her life due to a contract with a &quot;god.&quot; Collecting the souls of companions and utilizing artifacts and structures, aim for the deepest part of the dream to become the key to the contract!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >【Game Overview】</h2><strong>◆Let's Create a Labyrinth</strong><br>In the digging panels, various effects can be found, such as increasing companions, enhancing weapons, and healing. These panels also serve as resources that can give you an advantage in battles. Therefore, the timing of when to dig the panels becomes crucial.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398660/extras/a2903ead2228324c6c6fca2258b89975.poster.avif?t=1746058828\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398660/extras/a2903ead2228324c6c6fca2258b89975.webm?t=1746058828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398660/extras/a2903ead2228324c6c6fca2258b89975.mp4?t=1746058828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You can place units and structures in the dug locations. Choose routes according to the situation and create advantageous terrains that are unique to you.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398660/extras/9e9c0bff48c5e907f383fc87f85c390c.poster.avif?t=1746058828\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398660/extras/9e9c0bff48c5e907f383fc87f85c390c.webm?t=1746058828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398660/extras/9e9c0bff48c5e907f383fc87f85c390c.mp4?t=1746058828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>◆Unit Growth System</strong><br>The souls that become companions can choose from four initial classes: Swordsman, Archer, Mage, and Healer. By leveling up and stepping on panels, they can undergo a job change and become advanced classes.<br><br>Each class learns different skills and can equip different weapons, so strategically position and freely combine your team to annihilate enemies.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398660/extras/b9ea6ea743ec5336f3111f65f660a2e6.poster.avif?t=1746058828\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398660/extras/b9ea6ea743ec5336f3111f65f660a2e6.webm?t=1746058828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398660/extras/b9ea6ea743ec5336f3111f65f660a2e6.mp4?t=1746058828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>◆Artifact Enhancement</strong><br>The artifacts, which are fragments of long-gone minor gods, possess various effects and acquiring them brings about changes throughout the game. They allow you to strengthen units and status effects, improve deployment capacity and healing power, and build a unique setup tailored to your playstyle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398660/extras/a2d3366bfa15061761094809b9cff1b1.poster.avif?t=1746058828\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398660/extras/a2d3366bfa15061761094809b9cff1b1.webm?t=1746058828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398660/extras/a2d3366bfa15061761094809b9cff1b1.mp4?t=1746058828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>◆Eroding Enemies</strong><br>At first, enemies appear only on one tile, but after each battle, they start eroding the tiles and advancing towards your position. Being surrounded can put you at a disadvantage, so expand the panels continuously to avoid being cornered.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398660/extras/78055668f60219c4ce2887677c94a4ac.poster.avif?t=1746058828\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398660/extras/78055668f60219c4ce2887677c94a4ac.webm?t=1746058828\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2398660/extras/78055668f60219c4ce2887677c94a4ac.mp4?t=1746058828\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
